reviewText:
Set had four separate discs for each individuals collection.
This had a few of our favorite skits such as:
-Christopher Walken (more cowbell)
-Adam Sandler and Chris Farley "Lunch Lady"
-Living in a van down by the river
-Columbia Decaffeinated Coffee Crystals
-Chippendales dancer
-Many more!

Each disc played in great quality.  I would highly reccomend for a good laugh!
Many thanks! Just what I needed.

I bought this for Chris Farley and got the added bonus of all the others. I haven't watched anyone other than Farley yet, but he alone made this completely worth it. The DVD was used, which, I knew. Came in excellent shape.
This was a time when SNL was good, Now SNL sucks.
